![](index_files/figure-revealjs/example-dist-1.png){width=1800}
:::
:::


## Missing Completely at Random (MCAR)


::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code  code-line-numbers="1|4-9"}
set.seed(123)

attrition |>
  mutate(
    years_at_company = replace(
      years_at_company,
      runif(n()) < 0.5, NA
    )
  ) |>
  plot_satisfaction()
```

